      "author_association" : "NONE",
      "body" : "What you need to know is that the harddisk automatically goes into ReadOnly mode when an error occurs. If i were you i would delete every folder except your wallet.dat and \"start over\" with syncing, this is normally what -reindex does. I'd recommend that you do the initial sync on a laptop or computer, and then once it's done start using your pi instead and see if the error will occur. There's also a risk that your hard drive might be faulty, how old is it?",
